title: Prana Cozinha Vegetariana
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Fast food, Salad bar, Juice bar, Delivery, Take-out
description: Small vegetarian restaurant opened in early-2015 near Corcovado, which serves a creative, eclectic array of international cuisine. Vegans will find plenty of choices including juices, smoothies, sandwiches, salads, desserts. Also has gluten-free items. Lunch is served from 12-3pm and snacks from 3-6:30pm.
streetAddress: Rua Ererê, 11 D, Praça São Judas Tadeu, Cosme Velho
